thread.title: BRIEF-Telechoice International Posts‍ Q4 Profit Attributable S$5.0 Mln

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Telechoice International Posts‍ Q4 Profit Attributable S$5.0 Mln
text:
Feb 23 (Reuters) - Telechoice International Ltd:
* ‍Q4 REVENUE S$127.2 MILLION VERSUS S$117.7 MILLION * Q4 PROFIT ATTRIBUTABLE TO EQUITY HOLDERS S$5.0 MILLION VERSUS S$3.9 MILLION
* RECOMMENDED A FINAL DIVIDEND OF S$0.016 PER ORDINARY SHARE FOR FY2017
* 2018 FULL YEAR OPERATING PERFORMANCE IS EXPECTED TO BE LOWER THAN THAT OF LAST YEAR
* EXPECTS OPERATING PERFORMANCE FOR 1Q2018 TO BE MAINTAINED AS SAME PERIOD OF LAST YEAR​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
